  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6912944c-f0ef-4b56-b7e5-0e777d3ae62e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-821b737a-4d2e-436e-88f5-bec786da77a9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4d2e582b-16e9-4aac-9806-17b7e836434f\"><b>안녕하세요 남성역한의원,</b></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffef34;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5bb74e3a-4d38-45fe-a370-ab3b80d6e770\"><b> 이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f6da2957-e383-4e47-bb8a-2563cb5b399a\"><b>입니다!</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-6912944c-f0ef-4b56-b7e5-0e777d3ae62e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-efef6fc7-5e45-434f-a01e-1df4c223c78d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"11\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_11.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-02dae8ea-4d69-47d0-8051-d96b821b7690\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c2e6c4e8-ca8c-460e-8908-17dc28969bc3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8f1a6b0c-ea96-443d-a487-12ad5a319eab\">갱년기, 단순히 &#x27;나이가 들어서 겪는 변화&#x27;일까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c935c99d-08e2-4857-a12e-e53f0a3206d1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-81603b05-da05-4ed1-ac41-c675a9210ae2\">사실 갱년기는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b345e681-1ef9-4d58-9237-50d152ead4b6\"><b>몸과 마음이 급격히 바뀌는 시기</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3e3ceb63-c34f-46c3-8d41-3a68528ca69c\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-adb60bc9-cb63-4978-b994-ce72c6813305\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f9496c9c-1471-4fbc-8e3a-999f2417c8f9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3ff829b8-f3d9-4376-99d0-98219c07ce4a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-717517c9-4272-4c65-90e8-c906303ebfdf\">그래서 더더욱!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-060aa3d2-cdda-4e2b-ac9f-55393b1215fa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7d32ffac-9e44-4101-a0bf-5f5433c53b9a\"><b>내 체질에 맞는 보약</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-75050a0a-6709-4cfe-bada-2b6913883cb7\">으로 체력을 보완하고 감정을 안정시켜주는 것이 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2f24a122-3823-43c3-a197-cac1b58506ab\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2c3fb5d9-9205-4351-ac1d-c9160094b5c7\">한의학에서는 사람의 체질을 크게 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5941ec92-7f53-4313-a543-51e04fa2d7e2\"><b>태음인, 소양인, 소음인, 태양인</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5446babb-ad42-4c39-9d56-7714922057b8\">으로 나누며,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c50eaf0d-e9cd-4237-be9a-39a93e0440a4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-da79fdb7-3c5b-47f5-b6e2-8e65c44f61bc\">각 체질마다 겪는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c4f7a751-3e1b-4094-8532-1e3e0fbcd672\"><b>갱년기 증상도 다르고 필요한 보약도 다릅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-02dae8ea-4d69-47d0-8051-d96b821b7690\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-40b4b261-5925-4bdd-9d4d-8aaa2ef514ce\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-40b4b261-5925-4bdd-9d4d-8aaa2ef514ce\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0a673b2901d40d0c.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1900\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1900\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0a673b2901d40d0c.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0a673b2901d40d0c.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-40b4b261-5925-4bdd-9d4d-8aaa2ef514ce\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-1771dc7b-da25-48a7-b04b-83f94ea78a68\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-545ab532-7333-442d-af86-395778466ef6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d9398501-a564-4a14-a293-72ed3efede07\"><b>태음인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-33839ba9-a830-42dd-8e0e-6ed1c523978f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-acfc7c4e-18dd-42c5-b677-92575141fbdf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-24447356-fd93-4f94-bbf8-8b5e6fc36eeb\"><b>특징</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3281792b-a518-427e-892e-a04ac1833993\">: 체격이 크고 에너지가 많은 편이지만, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9af2a3fa-398c-4a2e-ae4a-cb0d188b5d31\"><b>갱년기엔 피로·무기력·고혈압 </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f648d638-07ca-4387-b92c-f1943384e798\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-065cfcc1-e782-4e17-a68d-7aedb8649b5b\"><b>등</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7c134130-206f-4947-a583-6850d8172546\">으로 나타나기 쉬움.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3415463b-940b-469a-a825-30d9dfaecd23\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3443dd58-2a50-49a0-a027-8d0bb011b6d5\"><b>추천 보약</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-053bd001-5009-405a-bdf9-2953fcc66132\">: </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ec0e66af-23eb-470c-b04d-e7c13e4e1311\"><b>간과 심장을 도와주는 보약</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-98e36b53-4168-4cd9-bc8f-20cec3d33594\">이 필요합니다. 대표적으로는 체내 노폐물 배출을 돕는 한약이나 혈압 조절을 돕는 처방이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-729ff9d8-d08d-4778-af12-bc1c1b728fb7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9fe67167-af13-40ed-b645-33deed7fbaa6\"><b>이런 증상이 있을 때</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a5f2efad-d932-4b23-9b1a-c972f1b64739\">: 기운이 없고 쉽게 짜증이 나거나, 혈압이 오르락내리락</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6a995ac1-0b34-464e-802a-5a6d11431257\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-262d9255-76d8-461e-a9e3-cb63e2cc7eae\">한다면 맞춤 보약으로 관리가 필요해요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-33839ba9-a830-42dd-8e0e-6ed1c523978f\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-3a4664ff-1c9e-430c-9a51-5b132f16b6b6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-left\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-64393419-851e-40c7-8700-d27cbcd9697a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-67608622-44d4-44b1-8605-1e9387ba8835\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a6568672-8e63-4ffa-b593-c9b9945f443a\"><b>소양인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-04dc468a-42c3-444d-b369-ad47887d7287\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1cba2fbd-579d-4004-8130-a57384942e59\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bb99aa7d-9a0d-4a04-8699-4e7e72458cfa\"><b>특징</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-41226248-a9bc-4b81-8d46-813fb6c42d4f\">: 체내 열이 많고, 갱년기에는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-22992af1-19d6-4f7f-8904-26ab03821761\"><b>불면, 가슴 두근거림, 안절부절못함</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bf57e7ce-96fb-49a4-8812-658035a9247f\"> 등이 자주 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f50c958c-5ebd-40a5-b964-41b5d8a67125\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7df748e3-1fb7-4168-8262-5207e34863d9\">생김.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6805dbf3-97a8-4142-b8ff-f09e0a26677c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-af9b17d7-236a-404b-9a20-e3cf3411e26c\"><b>추천 보약</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7e83c480-b24d-4161-bc16-708cda1db380\">: </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-293accca-d1b7-4eca-9307-db02167bb850\"><b>심열을 내려주고 정신을 안정시키는 한약</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d71c7ebe-d2a3-4cd8-a32e-5de3ab41d085\">이 효과적입니다. 스트레스를 줄여주는 처방이 핵심이에요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7af701db-db7c-4e5b-b186-07526517381a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fc1d8cad-398a-4a97-a4a9-c1234051438b\"><b>이런 증상이 있을 때</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-add642d4-4deb-470e-b80d-a8fcccab32ca\">: 자주 열이 오르고, 화가 많아지거나 잠을 잘 못 자면 체질에 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cf2f57d4-738f-442f-90a7-4b8b571bb6a1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3345dd16-4c27-41e3-8917-fae9d177083e\">맞는 진정 보약을 추천합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-04dc468a-42c3-444d-b369-ad47887d7287\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-5f975fdc-be26-4903-bad3-34834d62072e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-left\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-08f8ebc2-8a99-4f14-9465-65744a0eaf25\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1fdc95e8-2317-416f-b27e-7d61b133fc8c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2f9f0f78-e6f8-4dac-b124-f72dae18dd16\"><b>소음인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2f21bf29-ef72-4f76-9132-6531e5c09bf4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-864af92e-6c67-4177-b946-7761581a0058\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-04397435-1c9b-43ac-9cc4-cc9fdde21ec5\"><b>특징</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c7f8995d-249e-473c-a55e-a9380adcb657\">: 원래 체력이 약한 편이라 갱년기엔 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e846cc95-19ea-4710-8493-6077dedb0a5b\"><b>소화장애, 만성피로, 우울감</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-500b6aea-8152-46ff-aa72-a5741ca32e10\">으로 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-41a331b2-22ca-4044-b3ce-986a52b03e7f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6e45f655-0574-48d1-9922-4a7dc7d13467\">이어지기 쉬움.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9ab84850-3908-49df-abc9-30e0adc3da28\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1169f86e-2c18-4d9b-9dc0-4e378b5ae711\"><b>추천 보약</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4ed8b0dc-9d9a-49b8-a0bc-9e3434f63871\">: </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-17367ada-1a92-4f83-af10-21270de6617c\"><b>위장 기능을 돕고 기운을 북돋아주는 보약</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0cfe0c8e-83c4-4faf-abf9-8456eb3e98b4\">이 좋습니다. 몸이 따뜻해지고 기력이 회복되도록 하는 처방이 핵심이에요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-00fb0921-e3a9-4528-830b-20e7f8d709b1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5c300820-1376-45f6-ad6d-a60973db302a\"><b>이런 증상이 있을 때</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d56f28ea-f8a8-4f0b-ae00-ea5fb99a945f\">: 쉽게 지치고 우울감이 자주 찾아온다면 따뜻한 기운을 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6f58e223-881c-4c63-bb88-958f3fc37f62\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-62473e7c-a287-4b79-ad9e-c8a751270f42\">주는 보약으로 도와줄 수 있어요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-2f21bf29-ef72-4f76-9132-6531e5c09bf4\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-795bbad6-3183-422f-846a-3e7dfa765372\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-left\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-b39b4e96-db38-4e82-a424-4445be67daf8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9a54f51c-d1d5-458d-9118-a01bbad7bc8b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-22499a63-53b5-4c15-a7bc-a24ee7ccaebf\"><b>태양인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7cf6ae3b-0965-4c57-9f0f-8690a66bbf83\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fdb18066-800e-4672-ae9c-9b5669a44516\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-42524844-d0af-4c0d-96bd-32d3932b28bd\"><b>특징</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-14d0ff6f-af13-4d20-a177-f82894e5725e\">: 체질적으로 갱년기에 가장 불안정해지기 쉬운 타입. </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fd4842d2-3fda-445c-b740-328484d42ffb\"><b>눈, 간, 두통, 감정 기복</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9e7217c1-3975-4132-989b-db6c4a2e2a13\">이 심하게 올 수 있음.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e88aa647-64b1-434d-9c80-4fb6039ae61c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a033a03b-1de9-4744-ae34-8eccec5b277e\"><b>추천 보약</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e8efbb36-a242-45ae-b449-32eca112a857\">: </span><span style=\"\" c